programme.title: Aku Raja Lawak

programme.title: Bayangan Emilia
programme.desc: Rita berpindah masuk ke banglo Ungku Mahmud dan mula merasai akan kehadiran roh yang seperti tidak senang dengan kehadirannya disitu. Apakah misteri di sebalik rumah banglo tersebut?

programme.title: Oh Speak English Please

programme.title: Striker Hati Ayah
programme.desc: Sofia susah untuk memilih antara dua calon, Raf atau Noah. Lalu meminta pendapat ayahnya, Adam. Kini dua lelaki tersebut terpaksa memenangi hati ayah Sofia, seorang peminat fanatik bola.

programme.title: Gebu Gebu Manis
programme.desc: Kisah Hamdi dan Dolah yang memulakan perniagaan dodol tetapi sering disabotaj oleh Amira yang cemburu dengan perniagaan dua orang sahabat ini.

programme.title: Wartawan Kampung
programme.desc: Mustaqim yang tidak habis belajar, pulang ke kampung mewujudkan laman web kampung disokong Tok Ketua Kampung Kambing. Untuk mempopularkan laman web itu, Mak Jah dan Mak Temah dilantik menjadi wartawan kampung untuk bahagian berita gosip dan hangat yang merancang untuk merampas laman web itu untuk kepunyaan sendiri. Akhirnya, berita menjadi finah, kampung pula menjadi porak-poranda.

programme.title: Lukisan Cinta

programme.title: Perempuan Disarung Ungu

programme.title: Meniti Cinta Di Starimost

programme.title: Suamiku Encik Perfect 10!

programme.title: Kampung Kuala Lambat

programme.title: Musnahkan Pelamin Anganku

programme.title: Dua

programme.title: Racun Menantu

Morphle transforms into all the tools a good detective needs-a magnifying glass to find clues, a key to unlock secrets, and a cage to trap the culprit-in this exciting and magical mystery adventure.

programme.title: Morphle
programme.desc: From stopping bullies to fixing broken toys, theres no problem too big or small for Morphle! In this magical adventure, Milas pet morphs into all sorts of incredible things-a giant construction vehicle, a speeding race car, a mighty T-Rex-to help people and protect the city. Its a showcase of Morphles most amazing and heroic transformations.

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Lets learn about teeth and food! Join JJ to discover his favorite pizza toppings and then take a trip to a farm to count apples. After all that yummy food, learn how to take care of your teeth by brushing them well. When JJ gets nervous about a dentist visit, his siblings show him it can be fun. Plus, learn how to make a healthy and delicious frozen fruit treat!

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: If youre happy, sing along with JJ and friends! Enjoy story time with Little Bunny Foo Foo and sing about all the animals on Grandpas farm. Play with five little animals on a sleepy Saturday morning. Learn how to be brave on the playground, use your imagination with a pretend play song and discover all the cool shapes in your lunchbox. Its a day of happy songs and playful learning!

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Its time to sing along with JJ through a day of adventures! Join the exciting doggy hunt to find Bingo on his birthday. Use your imagination to play the floor is lava with the family. Learn how to take care of pets and see all the kids favorite toys during Play and Tell at school. Get a surprise visit from a real fire engine and join a Thanksgiving feast that celebrates family and friends.

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Get ready for playtime with JJ! Use your imagination to pretend youre a doctor, then become a hero and play firefighter. When JJ loses his teddy bear, the whole family helps him feel better. Have a thrilling balloon boat race on the farm and then go on a fun camping trip. Have a puppy playdate with Nina and Puddles and play a fun game of Simon Says at a family barbecue.

programme.title: Oddbods: Short
programme.desc: Welcome to the wonderfully weird world of the Oddbods! This collection of bite-size adventures follows seven colorful friends with very big, and very different, personalities. Whether its Fuses hot-headedness, Pogos pranks, or Zees laziness, their unique traits clash in spectacular fashion. Watch as simple, everyday situations spiral into unpredictable and hilarious mayhem, proving that with the Oddbods, life is never, ever dull.

programme.title: Minibods
programme.desc: Get ready for some pumpkin munch mayhem! Newt has grown a giant pumpkin for Halloween, but a hungry Wrigglepillar keeps trying to eat it. In a football game, Bubbles cheats to help her team win. Jeff is excited for a dancing game, but Fuse wont listen to the instructions and ruins the fun.

programme.title: Minibods
programme.desc: Get ready for a day of disasters! Newt is in a hurry to finish her drawing and accidentally harms a real flower. Lulu goes on a camping trip but has a disaster of her own when she realizes shes left her favorite bunny at home. Jeff causes his own trouble when he pretends to be sick to get attention from his friends.

programme.title: Minibods
programme.desc: Get ready to build a Snowbod! Pogo wants to show Lulu how fun snow can be, so they build a snowman together, but the sun comes out and starts to melt it! Lulu reads a story about a magical Snowhoof and sets off to find it in real life. On the ice, Fuse gets impatient when Jeff cant learn how to skate as quickly as the others.

programme.title: Little Baby Bum
programme.desc: Its time to learn about numbers, sounds and colors! The friends fly colorful fish kites at the park and bake some yummy cookies. They play with five little speckled frogs and five little green monster bottles. They learn about all the sounds that different vehicles make, how to say hello with a wave and what sounds different instruments make.

programme.title: Little Baby Bum
programme.desc: Get ready for a nursery rhyme fun time! The friends pretend to row their boats in laundry baskets. They do a fun Hop Little Bunnies dance and play Ring-A-Ring O Roses in the garden. They build a bridge with blocks and Mr. Giraffe takes them all for a ride on the bus. Plus, they help two little birds and have a parade with homemade instruments.

programme.title: Little Baby Bum
programme.desc: Its time to shake your little baby bum! The friends have a fun dance party in the park. The mummy monkeys teach the little ones a calming breathing song. The friends play in the sandpit and go on a fishing adventure. They play Jack and Jill, learn some cute actions from Grandma Panda and have a tea party. Its a day full of singing, dancing and playing!

programme.title: Go Buster
programme.desc: Get ready for fun and games with Buster! He gets caught in a storm but bravely rescues his friend Scout. He plays with balloons and floats high into the sky! He imagines hes a fish in the ocean and a cowboy in the Wild West. He even plays skittles, goes to a soft play center for hide and seek and helps stop a runaway train.

programme.title: Go Buster
programme.desc: Learn how to stay clean and healthy with Buster! When Buster gets stuck in the mud and then a slimy green puddle, he needs to go to the carwash to get clean. After getting a wobbly tooth from eating too many sweets, he learns about the importance of good dental hygiene. Plus, see what happens when Buster gets sick and his friend Scout fetches Amber the Ambulance to help him feel better.

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: Brother Hui, who runs an amphibian and reptile store in Xinxing District, Kaohsiung City, has a wide range of knowledge in the field of reptiles. He started with red-eared sliders and gradually got in touch with tortoises, lizards, snakes and other reptile pets. In Brother Huis brick-and-mortar store, the most special existence is the two store pets, the South American lizards. The male is called Meatball and the female is called Porkball. How did their fate with Brother Hui begin? Brother Hui, who has many years of experience in raising South American lizards, also generously share his breeding secrets. How to distinguish male and female South American lizards? How to keep them healthy? Whats the secret to taming them? In this epsiode, we unpack the living environment of South American lizards and reveal the breeding guide!

programme.title: ...Make You Laugh Out Loud
programme.desc: From the funniest feline fails, to the cutest of kittens weve dug out the very best the internet has to offer, and weve the cream of the crop right here.

programme.title: Cute Pet Guide
programme.desc: The meerkat king from "Madagascar" is funny, but meerkats in real life are well-behaved, cuddly and they heal our hearts! Pocket sized pets are currently all the rage, but there are details you need to pay attention to when raising them. For example, hedgehogs are highly defensive, timid sugar gliders will harm themselves without being next to their owners, and cute guinea pigs like Norman from the movie "The Secret Life of Pets" are easily abandoned due to being easy to obtain and raise, etc. Dont worry, experts will teach you how to raise them! Come to a restaurant in Kaohsiung to get up close with Rocket Raccoon from "The Avengers"!

programme.title: Zoo Vet At Large
programme.desc: Dr. Matt gets up close and personal with Albert, Flamingolands 12-foot alligator, as he moves to a new home. Teddy the pet sheep has suspected calcium deficiency and needs emergency treatment, and Marcel the marmoset leads Matt a merry dance around the surgery. Back at Flamingoland, a reluctant macaw needs his beak trimming -V and Matt comes face-to-face with the new pride of lions.

programme.title: The Dog Rescuers
programme.desc: In a very special festive edition of The Dog Rescuers, Inspector Lyndsey Taylor is called to a case of a desperate dog, left home alone at Christmas. With concern growing for the dogs health, can Lyndsey secure a warrant for police to enter the property in time?

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: Genus Pterophyllum, commonly known as P. scalare, freshwater angelfish or just angelfish is a large tropical fish native to the Amazon River in South America.They have a laterally flattened body, making them suitableto live in the crevices of tree roots in rivers with smooth water flow, and feeds on aquatic insects. The water temperature should be maintained at 26, and should reach 27-28 when breeding. The fertilized eggs are then released and attached to water plants or rocks, and the couple will take care of them together. However, once the eggs are hatched, the bigger ones will eat the smaller ones, hence not suitable to be raised together with other small fishes.

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: Genus Pterophyllum, commonly known as P. scalare, freshwater angelfish or just angelfish is a large tropical fish native to the Amazon River in South America.They have a laterally flattened body, making them suitableto live in the crevices of tree roots in rivers with smooth water flow, and feeds on aquatic insects. The water temperature should be maintained at 26, and should reach 27-28 when breeding. The fertilized eggs are then released and attached to water plants or rocks, and the couple will take care of them together. However, once the eggs are hatched, the bigger ones will eat the smaller ones, hence not suitable to be raised together with other small fishes.

Genara exige a Hilario Guanipa le diga en donde est su esposa Adelaida, pues ella sabe que la saco a la fuerza de su casa. Florencia le pide a su esposo le diga que ocurrio entre el y Victoria mientras se resguardaban de la lluvia; el aunque asegura que no la traiciono, considera que lo mejor para ellos es que se separen; sin embargo, ella no est dispuesta a darle el divorcio. A Hilario le avisan que algo ocurrio con Carlos Hansen y de inmediato se presenta en el hospital del pueblo a saber que paso; Felipe relata que tuvieron un accidente de trnsito y que su jefe tuvo que ser trasladado a la capital porque su estado es muy delicado. Hilario lleva a Adelaida hasta su casa; all Felipe, frente a Victoria y Genara, le informa a la seora que Hansen tuvo un accidente; Adelaida teme una desgracia.

Elda a solas, llorando, porque en el fondo no se siente feliz con lo que hizo. Sebastin, impactado, cuando Axel le confiesa que el hijo de Amelia es de el.

programme.title: Piel Salvaje - S01:E108
programme.desc: Max comunica a Camila que conoce el paradero de Rosa Blanco. Fausto disfruta vejando a Patricia y que pagar, como Rosa Blanco, por un crimen que no cometio. Alfredo va a hablar con Elda, la desprecia como madre la culpa y los remordimientos la atormentan: es parte de la venganza por su traicion a Rosa Blanco.

programme.title: El Desprecio - S01:E07
programme.desc: Tamara se presenta ante Clara Ines, quien se interesa en saber quien es la mujer.

programme.title: El Desprecio - S01:E08
programme.desc: Ral ha metido a varias amantes en su apartamento de soltero; en el corazon de Clara nace un nuevo sentimiento hacia Ral: el odio.

programme.title: Corazon Traicionado - S01:E08
programme.desc: Lorena resigns at the Corona house. Ricardo is still stunned by his mother about the million dollars they lost. Lorena; among the shelves of the antique shop discovers the figure of Gertrudis talking to the delinquent, thus confirming her terrible suspicion that it is Albertos own mother who wants to end the life of her husband, Marco Aurelio Corona.

programme.title: Te Tengo en Salsa - S01:E04
programme.desc: Despues de escoger la torta que le har Matilde, Beatrice revela a Adriana que Carlos Ral tiene novia desde hace muchos aos.

programme.title: Te Tengo en Salsa - S01:E05
programme.desc: Ignacio asume que se convertir en socio del Da Perroni aunque Salvatore tiene la sensacion de que cometio un gran error al aceptar la ayuda de su yerno.

programme.title: Te Tengo en Salsa - S01:E06
programme.desc: Una decidida Adriana amenaza con gritar si Carlos Ral no la suelta; este sella sus labios con un inesperado beso.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E099
programme.desc: Victoria Guanipa y Nicols Del Casal se despiden con un abrazo luego de pasar la noche juntos resguardndose de una fuerte tormenta cuando son sorprendidos Florencia de Del Casal, quien le reclama a su esposo su cercana con Victoria. Genara exige a Hilario Guanipa le diga en donde est su esposa Adelaida, pues ella sabe que la saco a la fuerza de su casa. Florencia le pide a su esposo le diga que ocurrio entre el y Victoria mientras se resguardaban de la lluvia; el aunque asegura que no la traiciono, considera que lo mejor para ellos es que se separen; sin embargo, ella no est dispuesta a darle el divorcio. A Hilario le avisan que algo ocurrio con Carlos Hansen y de inmediato se presenta en el hospital del pueblo a saber que paso; Felipe relata que tuvieron un accidente de trnsito y que su jefe tuvo que ser trasladado a la capital porque su estado es muy delicado. Hilario lleva a Adelaida hasta su casa; all Felipe, frente a Victoria y Genara, le informa a la seora que Hansen tuvo un accidente; Adelaida teme una desgracia.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E100
programme.desc: Frente a Hilario Guanipa, su hija Victoria y Genara, Felipe Osuna informa a Adelaida de Guanipa que Carlos Hansen sufrio un accidente, pero sigue con vida; el joven Osuna quiere darle a la seora un mensaje que su jefe le envio antes de lo ocurrido, pero la mujer, aturdida, sale corriendo de su casa sin escucharlo; Hilario ordena a todos que le dejen tranquila. Sintiendose culpable, Adelaida llora desconsolada creyendo a su amado Hansen en peligro de muerte cuando el hombre se aparece ante ella sano y salvo explicndole que todo fue una trampa que monto para distraer la vigilancia de Hilario y poder sacarla de la hacienda. Fernanda de Alcoy avisa a Florencia que ya tiene casi todo cuadrado para lo que van a hacer en contra de Victoria; Fernanda, quien se entero de que Victoria boto a su padre de su casa, avisa a Florencia que deben aprovechar esa oportunidad para llevar a cabo su plan contra la joven Guanipa y que toda la culpa recaiga sobre Hilario; la joven seora Del Casal le pide a su ta poltica le de dos das para prepararse para el evento.

programme.title: Piel Salvaje - S01:E109

Virginia does the math and realizes she is late on her menstrual period. Gertrudis tries to excite Patricia to win over Alberto.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E101
programme.desc: Para decidir quien comprar las yeguas, Florencia reta a Victoria a una carrera por el llano donde la ganadora se quedar con los animales; Victoria acepta el desafo. Una inesperada visita de Hilario asusta a Federico, mientras que Fernanda no se amilana y le recuerda a su medio hermano que Victoria es quien lo est dejando en la ruina; Hilario le asegura a Fernanda que no permitir que su propia hija lo despoje de lo que le pertenece. En medio de la carrera, Florencia desenfunda su arma y dispara al viento para obligar a Victoria a detenerse; esta ltima se extraa al ver a la seora Del Casal armada, dispuesta a matar, pero Florencia es incapaz de seguir su plan, por lo que decide terminar la carrera. Frente a un confundido Nicols, Victoria irrumpe en la hacienda Los Samanes para exigirle a Florencia una explicacion sobre el por que esta cavo una fosa cerca del lugar donde disparo durante la carrera: debido a que Florencia niega su participacion en la excavacion, Victoria arremete en contra de ella para que confiese su intencion de asesinarla.

programme.title: Piel Salvaje - S01:E110
programme.desc: Camila y su madre, en un emotivo encuentro, se unen en un abrazo anhelado durante tantos aos. Marcelina ronda por un parque aturdida, desequilibrada y nerviosa, luego de conocerse su traicion.

programme.desc: Para decidir quien comprar las yeguas, Florencia reta a Victoria a una carrera por el llano donde la ganadora se quedar con los animales; Victoria acepta el desafo. Una inesperada visita de Hilario asusta a Federico, mientras que Fernanda no se amilana y le recuerda a su medio hermano que Victoria es quien lo est dejando en la ruina; Hilario le asegura a Fernanda que no permitir que su propia hija lo despoje de lo que le pertenece. En medio de la carrera, Florencia desenfunda su arma y dispara al viento para obligar a Victoria a detenerse; esta ltima se extraa al ver a la seora Del Casal armada, dispuesta a matar, pero Florencia es incapaz de seguir su plan, por lo que decide terminar la carrera. Frente a un confundido Nicols, Victoria irrumpe en la hacienda Los Samanes para exigirle a Florencia una explicacion sobre el por que esta cavo una fosa cerca del lugar donde disparo durante la carrera: debido a que Florencia niega su participacion en la excavacion, Victoria arremete en contra de ella para que confiese su intencion de asesinarla.
